Package: deairdata
Title: API Wrapper to Access Air Data from the German Environment Agency
    (Umweltbundesamt)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Long", "Nguyen", , "long.nguyen@uni-bielefeld.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8878-7386"))
Description: Enables access to air quality data from the German
    Environment Agency via the Umweltbundesamt Air Data Public API
    (<https://www.umweltbundesamt.de/daten/luft/luftdaten/doc>).
